# Client Environment Configuration

# API URL - Change this to your computer's IP address when accessing from other devices
# Example: VITE_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:5000
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env (without .example)
# 2. Find your computer's IP address:
#    - Windows: Run 'ipconfig' in Command Prompt, look for IPv4 Address
#    - Mac/Linux: Run 'ifconfig' or 'ip addr', look for inet address
# 3. Replace localhost with your IP address in VITE_API_URL
# 4. Restart the development server
